title: Complete Final Fantasy OST sountracks and singles, properly tagg
description:
This is the complete collection of Final Fantasy sountracks, singles, piano collections, etc.

70 albums/singles total.

Being a big fan of Nobuo&#039;s work, I stopped collecting after XI since, in my personal opinion, the music has just lacked something since then.

Everything is properly tagged in both IDv1 and IDv2, track numbers are all included as well as album names. Each album/single is in it&#039;s own separate folder.
